OL,3,CWarning to 'keep windows shut' after
OL,4,Cindustrial estate fire
OL,6,FFire crews remain at the scene of a
OL,7,Fhuge fire which broke out at an
OL,8,Findustrial estate in a Welsh village.
OL,9,FResidents in Pontllanfraith, near
OL,10,FBlackwood in Caerphilly county, have
OL,11,Fbeen asked to keep their windows and
OL,12,Fdoors closed and avoid the area due to
OL,13,Fthe ongoing incident.
OL,15,FSouth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,16,Fwas called to a large blaze at
OL,17,FCommercial Street, Pontllanfraith
OL,18,Fshortly before 6pm on Monday evening.
OL,19,FIt said a two-storey building
OL,20,Fcontaining multiple businesses was
OL,21,F"well alight" when they arrived.
