OL,3,CWarning to 'keep windows shut' after
OL,4,Cindustrial estate fire
OL,6,FA statement said: "We advise residents
OL,7,Fin the local area to keep windows and
OL,8,Fdoors closed due to large amount of
OL,9,Fsmoke in area. Thank you for your
OL,10,Fpatience and cooperation while we deal
OL,11,Fwith this incident."
OL,13,FAn update from the fire service added:
OL,14,F"The stop message has not yet been
OL,15,Fgiven and a fire investigation will be
OL,16,Fcarried out."
