OL,3,CWarning to 'keep windows shut' after
OL,4,Cindustrial estate fire
OL,6,FFire crews used specialist equipment
OL,7,Fincluding aerial ladder platforms and
OL,8,Fwater bowers to tackle the blaze at
OL,9,Fthe industrial estate, which consists
OL,10,Fof multiple businesses in a 2-storey
OL,11,Fproperty.
OL,13,FCrews and appliances from Aberbargoed,
OL,14,FCaerphilly, Risca, Treharris,
OL,15,FAbercynon, Roath, Tonypandy,
OL,16,FAbertillery, Aberbargeod and Cardiff
OL,17,FCentral were among those who attended
OL,18,Fthe scene.
